creator: JRJ Unlimited
descriptionHtml:
There are 99 free cartoon sound effects that are loud and clear.

These free high volume cartoon sounds are perfect for notifications, ringtones or alarms.

Use this application as a soundboard. Simply press each button to listen and preview the loud and clear ringtone or sound.

Once you find a sound or song that you like, press and hold the button to save. Select either ringtone, alarm, notification, or contact.

Download now and you can set a cartoon sound for each individual in your contacts so you will know who is calling without even looking!

This application can be used with most phones or tablets and can be used for ringtones or notifications or alarms.

This easy and free application allows you to make your phone or tablet very unique.

Best of all this application is free!

According to our many users the best cartoon sounds are:
* Arrows
* Laugh
* Tip Toe
* Rock Fall
* Voices

You are not limited to the notifications, alarms and ringtones that come with your device. Use this application to make your device your own.
